name: | ROBO WARRIORS | Buta Hejo
description:
Buta Hejo
weapon : Spears, twin axes, laser cyclops
power : 5/5
defence : 2/5
soul : 5/5

story :
The titan abandoned by his parents and raised by good humans blinded Hejo to have human-like feelings and titan-like powers, making him the perfect combination to fight the forces of evil. His childhood surrounded by non-toxic society made him happy even though he lost his parents and promised to devote his life to peace on earth.
